{"tid":890562,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【逼爆東涌】香港電台發現有支那旅行社辦大橋來回東涌一日遊","createTime":"2018-11-05T11:51:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-10T03:59:14.000Z","uid":79563,"like":16,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"098993be91d2e48d9ea195e35e4513fee6b54eac","tid":890562,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T11:51:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1426738_1_L_20181105183336.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1426738_1_L_20181105183336.jpg&h=29a6c186&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n港珠澳大橋開通後令到東涌商場及食肆的迫滿大量內地旅客，有東涌居民話，旅客隨地丟棄垃圾，影響環境衛生。<br />\n<br />\n旅遊業議會主席黃進達相信，昨日有過千名內地旅客，並沒有向議會登記經港珠澳大橋入境，他們由於沒有特定行程，於是在東涌聚集，即日返回支那。<br />\n<br />\n本台記者以旅客身份，向支那旅行社查詢，發現有不少以公共交通工具來回東涌至大橋的一日團。"},{"pid":"8de487215f6c3baf6b68b51c9a6c4d668fc52e20","tid":890562,"uid":26506,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T12:03:43.000Z","msg":"Link?"},{"pid":"182fa45ee02bbac2a07c42ab4836dd66befef260","tid":890562,"uid":21378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T12:55:05.000Z","msg":"東涌以前有食街,之後裝修冇咗, 依家重有冇"},{"pid":"3d3ebbd5a8c55aa6768449395d0e188a80ac6689","tid":890562,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8de487215f6c3baf6b68b51c9a6c4d668fc52e20","tid":890562,"uid":26506,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T12:03:43.000Z","msg":"Link?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T17:29:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1426738-20181105.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1426738-20181105.htm&d=PjAGIXuhr%2FYv5tc13vOj9zA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=f467c76a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1426738-20181105.htm&h=0f7df47a\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1426738-20181105.htm</a>"},{"pid":"1af26c7d8ee82d81183be991a228ff1fb499cf50","tid":890562,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T17:30:19.000Z","msg":"邱騰華：近日部分內地團未必符合規定已向內地跟進　<br />\n<br />\n港珠澳大橋過去一個周末再有大批旅客輪候過境巴士，正在上海的行政長官林鄭月娥表示，每個大型基建一開通時都會有問題，有關部門特別是運輸及房屋局以及運輸署已不斷作出應變，希望未來大橋會更暢順。<br />\n<br />\n商務及經濟發展局局長邱騰華表示，大橋開通後在附近地區的內地人來港是好事，應該歡迎，但留意到有內地居民參加的旅行團未必完全符合規定，商經局已同內地有關單位提出，強調會依法工作，亦與內地商討加強宣傳。"},{"pid":"2114995bf4f643deb8405066ddbb965670f9121f","tid":890562,"uid":12021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T17:31:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f4632921fd98dae4d3d43f7fe839c9209e0bcbda","tid":890562,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"182fa45ee02bbac2a07c42ab4836dd66befef260","tid":890562,"uid":21378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T12:55:05.000Z","msg":"東涌以前有食街,之後裝修冇咗, 依家重有冇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T18:51:42.000Z","msg":"就算有都唔會做香港人生意"},{"pid":"7e50c0a5fa39d8b2412bdefa9fb3071b47d0bbd0","tid":890562,"uid":16676,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T18:54:38.000Z","msg":"旅行社咁樣做生意都有<br />\n叫d 客搭公共交通, 去妨礙其他人使用<br />\n<br />\n唔好話商業責任同道德<br />\n即情做人既規矩都無<br />\n<br />\n呢個世界只有支那旅行社先會敢咁樣做<br />\n仲要d 客ok 先出奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92386398d1287848affa74ef11923d04ad30a3d6","tid":890562,"uid":47674,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T21:53:04.000Z","msg":"不是旅行團<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我們是民眾自發集體旅遊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"659a6770fa495dd7d594b74cd90f182abdf0a90a","tid":890562,"uid":51701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"92386398d1287848affa74ef11923d04ad30a3d6","tid":890562,"uid":47674,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T21:53:04.000Z","msg":"不是旅行團<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />